data.description: AMAZING DEAL! WELL KEPT HOME! Inviting home featuring an entry foyer that opens into a large family room with separate dining space, and good sized kitchen with stainless steel appliances and center island. This home has a fantastic flow! Wood look luxury vinyl plank throughout the home. Owners suite at back of the home with large walk in closet. Two additional bedrooms share a full bath. Large flat rear yard perfect for play. This Smarthome features the Ring doorbell, Wifi throughout the home, smart thermostat, and smart Garage openers.Full irrigation system for front and back yards.  Enjoy amenities such as a pool, playground, picnic area, and a community center. With downtown Austin just a 28-minute drive away, convenient access to the toll road, shopping, restaurants, and the ACC Campus awaits. Embrace the comfort of living in a small community while having easy access to everything Austin has to offer.
